@startuml
actor Client
boundary "Qualifications Management API" as System

== Get All Qualifications ==
Client -> System : GET /api/qualifications
System --> Client : 200 OK\nList<QualificationDto>

== Get Qualification By ID ==
Client -> System : GET /api/qualifications/{id}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nQualificationDto\nOR 404 Not Found

== Get Qualification By Code ==
Client -> System : GET /api/qualifications/code/{code}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nQualificationDto\nOR 404 Not Found

== Get Qualification By Name ==
Client -> System : GET /api/qualifications/name/{name}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nQualificationDto\nOR 404 Not Found

== Create Qualification ==
Client -> System : POST /api/qualifications\nBody: CreatingQualificationDto
System --> Client : 201 Created\nQualificationDto

== Update Qualification ==
Client -> System : PATCH /api/qualifications/{id}\nBody: CreatingQualificationDto
System --> Client : 200 OK\nQualificationDto\nOR 404 Not Found

@enduml
